Package: wUMAP
Title: Variance-Weighted PCA UMAP for Seurat Objects
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides RunWeightedUMAP(), a drop-in replacement for Seurat
    RunUMAP() where each principal component axis is scaled by a weight
    derived from its percentage of explained variance before manifold
    learning.
